{"tid":473825,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【科技要聞】英國著名物理學家霍金成功研發全球首部時光輪椅","createTime":"2017-11-19T14:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T15:36:16.000Z","uid":30836,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ecfd62deb4e32bc1e995bbc78dc4dc22d254004f","tid":473825,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://sciencevibe.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/hawkingtiemtravel.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsciencevibe.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2Fhawkingtiemtravel.jpg&h=0773b689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>霍金成功研製全球首部時光輪椅，物理學家霍金（前排右二）指，下一步會朝時光步行輔助器方向發展。</em><br />\n<br />\n【南荒日報報導】電動輪椅近年在香港以至世界各地迅速發展，霍金與其科研團隊早前亦成功研發全球首部時光輪椅，昨日首在劍橋大學「老人日」亮相，該輪椅配備時空移位器，可在既定時空自由奔走之餘，也能迴避絕大部份因蝴蝶效應所構成的時空不連續性，造價只約港幣三萬元。"},{"pid":"687c2b6299e83e9a37085f55327753931a3f5ea2","tid":473825,"uid":75156,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:26:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/222623_5de9ec47a8511885cc4e31c0ad5e4cd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F222623_5de9ec47a8511885cc4e31c0ad5e4cd8.jpg&h=06d31a70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪呢張？"},{"pid":"465a36f8db7ff3fc815e525af5ff258315415cb6","tid":473825,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:58:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/222623_5de9ec47a8511885cc4e31c0ad5e4cd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F222623_5de9ec47a8511885cc4e31c0ad5e4cd8.jpg&h=06d31a70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪呢張？</blockquote><br />\n你問霍金"},{"pid":"f69fa6f5c90f2c1b22ee86d8c708eb61bd245083","tid":473825,"uid":126615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T15:00:06.000Z","msg":"南荒日報"},{"pid":"1ca02a6a8d4c6c0cbcfbf7d